                                                  java.util.List<java.lang.String> removeProperties)
                                           throws java.io.IOException
Build WebDAV PROPPATCH entity.

Creates a Propertyupdate element containing all properties to set from setProps and all properties to remove from removeProps. Note this method will use a DEFAULT_NAMESPACE_URI as namespace and DEFAULT_NAMESPACE_PREFIX as prefix.

Parameters:
addProperties - Properties to add
removeProperties - Properties to remove
Returns:
The XML body

java.io.IOException - When there is a JAXB error
